'''百老匯網路資料庫'''（{{lang-en|'''Internet Broadway Database'''}}，简称'''IBDB'''）是一个关于[[百老匯劇院|百老匯劇院]]戏剧作品和其工作人员的在线[[数据库|数据库]]。持有者为{{link-en|百老汇联盟|The Broadway League}}。<ref name="IBDB">{{cite web |author=  |url= http://www.ibdb.com/index.php |title= Official Website IBDB.com |work=  |accessdate= 2012-26-07 |date=  |archive-date= 2012-07-25 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20120725083741/http://ibdb.com/index.php |dead-url= no }}</ref>该网站也有相应的IOS和Android应用程序。<ref name="Ticket News">{{cite web|author= |url= http://www.ticketnews.com/news/the-broadway-league-develops-IBDB-application0312595|title= The Broadway League develops IBDB application|work= |accessdate= 2012-26-07|date= |archive-date= 2016-02-18|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20160218051948/http://www.ticketnews.com/news/the-broadway-league-develops-IBDB-application0312595|dead-url= no}}</ref><ref name="Stage Directions">{{cite web|author= |url= http://www.stage-directions.com/theatre-buzz/4008-broadway-league-releases-ibdb-app-for-ios-devices.html|title= Broadway League Releases IBDB App for iOS Devices|work= |accessdate= 2012-26-07|date= |archive-date= 2019-10-29|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20191029134332/http://stage-directions.com/theatre-buzz/4008-broadway-league-releases-ibdb-app-for-ios-devices.html|dead-url= no}}</ref><ref name="Travel Writers Magazine">{{cite web|author= |url= http://travelwritersmagazine.com/broadway-leagues-new-ibdb-app-for-iphone-ipad-and-ipod-touch-links-theatergoers-with-centuries-of-theater/|title= Broadway League’s New IBDB App for iPhone, iPad and iPod Touch Links Theatergoers with Centuries of Theater|work= |accessdate= 2012-26-07|date= |archive-date= 2018-07-04|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20180704034944/http://travelwritersmagazine.com/broadway-leagues-new-ibdb-app-for-iphone-ipad-and-ipod-touch-links-theatergoers-with-centuries-of-theater/|dead-url= yes}}</ref>

网站提供了纽约戏剧的开端18世纪到今天为止的百老汇戏剧制作的记录。包括详细信息，相关的人以及有趣的事实和作品统计。 IBDB还拥有从过去到现在的百老汇戏剧制作的大部分存档照片。作品网页上同时提供歌曲在iTunes上的录音链接列表，奖项和提名的列表，评论，链接到Amazon.com购买商品，当前和历史演员名单。该网页包括剧院，人物，奖项，歌曲，和总票房的高级搜索选项。在未来IBDB将包括百老汇巡回演出中的数据，以及当前百老汇的信息。<ref name="Columbia Eresource">{{cite web |author=  |url= http://www.columbia.edu/cu/lweb/eresources/databases/5256819.html |title= Columbia University Library Eresources Database: IBDB |work=  |accessdate= 2012-26-07 |date=  |archive-date= 2013-01-16 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20130116135319/http://www.columbia.edu/cu/lweb/eresources/databases/5256819.html |dead-url= no }}</ref>

